make a O-RU branch, maybe master or p2018_zcu102 branch

將make好的O-RU放入SD Card，再放入板子裡面做開機，其中需注意三個必要程式BOOT.BIN、images.ub、root_final

接著將 oam_agent folder and synergy_stack folder 放入/opt中

至 /opt/synergy_stack/oam_sysrepo/yangmodel 執行command安裝欄位 ./install_ru_schema.sh  

至 /opt/synergy_stack/oam_sysrepo/config 執行command設定參數 ./import_ru_config.sh

至 /opt/oam_agent 執行 ./oam_agent.sh

正常會顯示

kpishm: attach kpi shm.
run all processesrun /opt/oam_agent/oam_ofh_test
Succeed to attach share memory.
